<definition-item><classification-symbol scheme="cpc">B21G1/00</classification-symbol><definition-title>Making needles used for performing operations  (forming heads on pin-like needles <class-ref scheme="cpc">B21G3/12</class-ref>; making U-shaped hairpins <class-ref scheme="cpc">B21G7/04</class-ref>)</definition-title><definition-statement>
      <section-title>Definition statement</section-title>
      <section-body><paragraph-text type="preamble">This place covers:</paragraph-text>
        <paragraph-text type="body">Devices and processes for making needles. The feature of the title &#8220;for performing operations&#8221; does not imply any particular restriction.</paragraph-text>
